                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18260112-119-off672 t18260112-119-cd673"></join>, 4 shirts, value 12s.; 4 cravats, value 4s.; 7 handkerchiefs, value 3s., and 13 pairs of stockings, value 4s.
            </rs> the goods of 
               <persName id="t18260112-119-victim671" type="victimName">
                  Joseph 
                  Claughton
               <interp inst="t18260112-119-victim671" type="surname" value="Claughton"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18260112-119-victim671" type="given" value="Joseph"></interp>
